Package com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.apigateway

Class ApiRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.apigateway.ApiRequest
  • public class ApiRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a request being sent to Amazon Api Gateway, including the parameters being sent as part of the request, the endpoint to which the request should be sent, etc.
